{"tid":1858210,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【緊急】美孚手足唔好再幫班藍絲自私撚","createTime":"2020-02-02T14:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T16:12:36.000Z","uid":230298,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"72bba127934414583682e66f28fbb6e7e0752649","tid":1858210,"uid":230298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T14:40:42.000Z","msg":"呢兩日為左個垃圾隔離營咬左咁多手足，而班藍絲仲係屋企大叫警察加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手足頭先係咁叫樓上居民落黎幫手都無人落<br />\n<br />\n既然班藍絲都接受起一個隔離營係自己屋企隔黎，<br />\n你爭取成功佢地都唔會多謝你<br />\n問真個句，值唔值得再為班自私撚咬多10幾個手足？ <br />\n班藍絲針唔到肉都唔知死<br />\n個隔離營聽日就啟用，俾佢地自己享受返個病毒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e97ca3681b2da07e5aeb2e8b9b374aba41f3697","tid":1858210,"uid":230298,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T14:44:23.000Z","msg":"兩晚過去佢地都無動於衷，<br />\n反正個病毒大部分重症、危殆都係班廢老<br />\n求下你地唔好為左班自私撚而再損失戰力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f6b5077b493120d5b9cc0f2eb3920e36f5dd8f","tid":1858210,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T14:50:07.000Z","msg":"如果有勇武居民真係好無助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40940d3af6d7222a42e69c9cdc27b0a98b19c878","tid":1858210,"uid":207902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T16:12:36.000Z","msg":"推"}]}